Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,== Dialogue ============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All you, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Five seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...connect the puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dream finally came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Time for our Victory Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are Smile Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher pulled Mana aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do this time, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! It was committee stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's {\i1}senbei {\i0}are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk with your mouth full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Want tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.93,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}--Gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.86,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! Nothing says springtime\Nof youth like sweat and sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our embroidery club counts, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's existed\Nsince Grandma's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stitch by stitch, we've made\Nmasterpieces across generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We all share a common thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. As president of such a\Ntime-honored club, quit talking and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya, let her drink tea in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on her, Kao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's a tough one today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what makes it\Nfulfilling when you finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a sense of accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! You've got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up. I'm image training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For embroidery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Mami! You get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Stop humoring her, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's so pretty! That's Mami for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In comparison, yours looks crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called being bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours doesn't even match the pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called being unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a neat color choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giddy when Mami praises you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today! Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's a stitch I kinda need\Nhelp with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's do our thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Soakin' it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An open-air bath whenever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perks of being friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! They wanna film at our {\i1}ryokan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For a drama? A movie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A variety show, or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean by, "or something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom got so excited by the call,\Nshe can't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're mailing the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think it's a TV\Nspecial about you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:08.74,Alternate,,0,0,0,,--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute Next-Gen Hostesses\Nof an Age-Old {\i1}Ryokan{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, "Newbie Hostesses at Work."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sorta shows are trending!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--They sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure we're here for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For "Cute Hostesses and Their\NSupport Crew," or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to say "cute hostesses."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the producer must have\Na good eye to pick our {\i1}ryokan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spouting more self-praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I "sing" my own praises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Strawberries from Yanagida\NFarms are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And super sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I could eat a million!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. My dad would be\Nhappy to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Stop chowing 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one dousing 'em\Nin condensed milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It overpowers the strawberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr! The milk elevates\Nthe strawberry taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In perfect sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? How about strawberries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat 'em plain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With condensed milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Very curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was late today 'cuz I got asked to\Nput something on the bulletin board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey hands-on trial class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikko's pro team, the Dream Monkeys,\Nis putting it on this Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You two can skate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it in gym class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it sound cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be worth trying out, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey, huh? That sounds pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't we get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! It'll be an experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma always says,\N"Try new experiences!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I doubt she meant ice hockey by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it might be fun to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's worth a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up for trying it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?! Let's do it, Mami!\NLet's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! I'll give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That settles it! I'll apply for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Once you wrap the thread, use\Nyour left hand to pull and right to push.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Thanks, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You're so\Npassionate about learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a project I'm trying to\Nfinish before second semester ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't focus too hard\Nor your eyes will go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Let's play again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been here\Nsince our gym field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When does ice hockey season start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz Ayaka overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! You wouldn't get up\Nso I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough excuses! C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Let's start\Nthis season with spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be kind! Make 'em think:\N"I wanna come back next week!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts with: "Ice hockey is kinda fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then: "Maybe I'll go next week!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough: "Maybe I'll join the\NDream Monkeys!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.07,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Understand?! You need to be super nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.66,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}--This is what you've been training for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Um, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a face\Nthat'll scare 'em away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! I've got wrinkles here?! Since when?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your issue? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko, they're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Sato, put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for the trial class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Kirifuri Arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Kinugawa Junior High\N3rd year, Manaka Mizusawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko Yanagida, Mami Ono,\Nand 2nd year, Ayaka Mizusawa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming to the ice hockey trial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Brr!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Change into your gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you guys participating\Nin the trial class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Manaka Mizusawa,\Na 3rd year at Kinugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko Saginuma from Kirifuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's my extra, Naomi Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're 3rd years, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me an extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! It's all girls this year!\NAnd what a harvest at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In junior high, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine! It's an early harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, my ambition will come to light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, that one idea of mixing\Nice hockey and entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! First, I'll train the girls to play\Nlike proper Dream Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But after each win, they'll do\Na victory dance on the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a clever performance\Nwill delight the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll bring in people who never\Nhad interest in ice hockey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll appear in my old uniform\Nand sing a song while I'm at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attract the biggest\Ncrowds you've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,More like your delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying some pretty crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't you dare\Nlet these girls slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, we'll start with warm-ups\Nto help prevent injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stretch along to a rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey uses a lot of muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do upper body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--One, two, three, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.39,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Interesting stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.57,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Two, two, three, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.59,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one more useful for games. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:20.30,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--This clearly isn't a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.66,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}--Two, two, three, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:24.73,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't a step!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dance\Nused to evade defenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--She said "dance" clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.97,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}--Four, five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.08,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One, two, three, four
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.38,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.37,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Everyone's keeping up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.65,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}On to the next dance routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've\Nwarmed up, let's get you on the rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can change into\Nyour uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this way. {Join if unnecessary}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah. (comment){C'mon, let's go. (???)}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--We get to wear uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that phony\Nstretch dance thing was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it went any longer, I would've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now. The fun's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's lighter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can move easy in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone\Nruns into you, won't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. In girls' hockey, body checking\Nis an illegal hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel stoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The trial class\Nstarts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rock and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rock and roll"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe to say everyone can skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That's the locals for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird skating in gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Ayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is edge control!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Control it! Go slow if needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, you've warmed up to the rink
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's talk about the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Games last for 60 minutes,\Nbroken into three, 20-minute periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Two teams compete to score\Nthe most goals in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There're two pieces of\Nequipment you need to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is a puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You score\Nby hitting it in the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about as big as a {\i1}jingoro senbei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of black rubber\Nand is very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sorry if it\Nhits you, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I don't wanna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko, what are you scaring 'em for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a hockey stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a bath-stirring stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You use the stick to control\Nthe puck by moving it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you guys try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Nobody's good at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone get in a circle\Nand practice passing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice stop, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys did great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of hockey?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was rusty since I haven't skated\Nin a while, but it came back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm new to using a stick,\Nbut it was kinda fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad we couldn't play more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you to show up next week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for "okey-dokey."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so old-fashioned, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful heading home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The hours just flew by!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! It was over before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you'll come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing the puck around...\NEveryone chasing after it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love embroidery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stitch by stitch,\Nwatching a project come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's such a sense of accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, connecting the puck\Naround was really neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For us to work together like that...\NIt was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play ice hockey next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're the one saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again next week, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, I--no, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered\Nour sparkling springtime of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect the puck, even in a game!
